<h3>How to Play ujas LittleSheep 1.5</h3><h4>A Mixture of a Board Game and an Arcade Game</h4>
<p>You are a shepherd had have to guide your sheep to juicy flowers, afterwards to th stable before time runs out.<br>
If you saved less than the half of the herd, your carreer as a shepherd is over. You even loose the points scored 
in this level.<br>
You get 100 points for each eaten flower, and 20 points for each sheep in the stable.</p>

<p>Take care of the terrain!<br>
The sheep are able to swim, but no further than 2 fields.<br>
Facing a fence they try to escape to the left or to the right, well, mostly...<br>
Beware of the moskitoes!</p>

<p>You guide your sheep with signposts/arrows. Put them onto the meadow (and only on the meadow), wehre you want the sheep to change directions.<br> You may turn your signposts by clicking on them. Once set, you can't remove signposts.</p>
<p>If you are stuck with some sheep, you may slaughter them, but take care that enough sheep have reached the stable!</p>
 
<p>If you scored enough points, you may enter your name in a highscore list.</p>
