<h4>Menus 4 and 5: Continue a Saved Game/ Save Game</h4>
<p>You have 8 slots to store/ retreive a game.</p>
<p>The slots save the current level and the score you got upto the last succesfuly completed level.</p>
<p>After retreiving this game, you start with its current level and the score you reached upto this level.</p>
<hr>

<h4>Highscore List Remarks:</h4>
<p>You may change the paths to the highscore lists in the file hiscore.ini.<br>
The first entry is meant for the local list, the second for a network list.
You must have read and write permission for this directory.<p>
<p>Before you first use a highscore list, you must reset it (Menu2 - Highscoee).</p>

